    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Economic and political system in which land and capital goods are publicly owned, and the governing authorities control the means of production, prices, and distribution.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
